# rebuild/ is a Cargo workspace; only the build output is ignored — Cargo.lock is committed
# (this workspace ships binaries, so a reproducible lockfile is the desired default).
target/
**/*.rs.bk
# proptest persists failing-case seeds next to the test binary; these are byproducts of a failed
# run (incl. transient red→green proofs), not source. Ignore them so they can't be staged by accident.
**/*.proptest-regressions
**/proptest-regressions/
